{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC01_WIL_420.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x39,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "So then I totally thought it was gonna be a big one, so I started digging it up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "But then, it was only this long...<CR>I was so disappointed!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha, yeah that happens sometimes. It's hard to tell how long a root is from above the ground."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "On the other hand, sometimes you can dig a whole as deep as you are tall, and the root is still growing further down."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Yup, yup. Gathering medicinal herbs sure makes you think. Oh, that reminds me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Last time, I went out a bit further than usual to find some medicinal herbs..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "And I found a good spot that no one knows about. I'll take you to it next time!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Really? Yay, that's exciting!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x81,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "...Hey, that's booorrring!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x84,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "What's fun about youthful girls talking about roots in the middle of the day!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Haha, sorry, we got carried away."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Jeez. Let's talk about something else."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "For example, how about...that new pastry shop!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Ooh, I know about that shop!<CR>It's really good!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "So you've tried it too, Nio? Yup, yup, their cakes are scrumdiliumptious!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "The mountain strawberry cake is the best one they have. Have you had it yet?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Mountain strawberry? No, I haven't.<CR>How about you, Nio?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I haven't, either.<CR>Hmm, mountain strawberries..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "They're so hard to gather."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Oh? Why's that?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "They grow in really-hard-to-get places, like the middle of a cliff or at the tops of trees."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Ohhh, I see."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "And they're always far from towns,<CR>so just going there is a pain."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "I see..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I've always wanted to use them for synthesis, but I've never had the chance."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "I've been interested in mountain strawberries, since they can also be used as an ingredient in medicine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x13c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, but that might be hard unless you can fly or something."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Hmph..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x13e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Wilbell, your cheeks are all puffed up! What's wrong?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Jeeeez! You guys are talking about plants again!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x80,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "Don't talk about stuff I don't know about!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "Ohhh, sorry, Wilbell.<CR>We didn't do it on purpose."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, when we're both together, we unconsciously start talking about things like that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x14,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x22,
            "msg_string": "Sorry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x23,
            "msg_string": "Sorry."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd0,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x24,
            "msg_string": "Hmph, fine. It's not like I'm your sister to begin with."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x25,
            "msg_string": "You sisters can keep on having fun like that. Yeah, be that way..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd1,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x26,
            "msg_string": "Ayesha, you should just selfishly keep having fun with Nio all day long..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x27,
            "msg_string": "Uh-oh, Wilbell has the pouty pouts..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x28,
            "msg_string": "Cheer up, Bell. Oh, I know!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x29,
            "msg_string": "You can start calling me \"Sis\" from now on!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2a,
            "msg_string": "Yeah! Then I'll start calling Wilbell, Sis!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xd2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2b,
            "msg_string": "Hmph. That's not the problem!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2c,
            "msg_string": "Kyah, I'm sorry..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2d,
            "msg_string": "Okay, you guys are forbidden from being friendly with each other!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2e,
            "msg_string": "What!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2f,
            "msg_string": "Since you guys are too close,<CR>there's no way I can join."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x30,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... I don't think Sis and I are that close..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x31,
            "msg_string": "I think we're about normal."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x32,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, like normal siblings."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x33,
            "msg_string": "Then be on bad terms. Then it'll be perfect for you guys."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x34,
            "msg_string": "Th-That's kinda hard to do..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x35,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, we can't just start fighting for no reason..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x36,
            "msg_string": "Ugh! Goodness! Anyways, I don't wanna be the only one who feels left out!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x37,
            "msg_string": "Um, um, then let's go gather medicinal herbs next‐"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7f,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x38,
            "msg_string": "NO to that, too!<CR>I forbid all medicinal herbs, too!"
        }
    ]
}